	<article id="article-2576329" data-id="2576329" data-paid="false" data-fullcontent="true" class="print" data-facebook-link="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A//china.hket.com/article/2576329%3Fr%3Dcpsdfb">
		<div class="article-detail">
			<div class="article-detail_title">
				<h1>【新冠肺炎】打臉特朗普！新冠肺炎與流感有5大不同　且危險性更高</h1>
			</div>

			<div class="article-details-info-container">
				<span class="hket-color-default"><span data-icon="&#xe911;" class="hket-icon-channel"></span> 社會熱點</span>
				<span class="article-details-info-container_date">
					<span class="font-en">20:19</span>
					<span class="font-en">2020/02/28</span>
				</span>
				<span class="article-details-info-container_facebook-like-container">	<div class="fb-like" data-href="https://china.hket.com/article/2576329/【新冠肺炎】打臉特朗普！新冠肺炎與流感有5大不同　且危險性更高" data-layout="button_count" data-action="like" data-show-faces="false" data-share="false" data-width="90" ></div>
</span>
			</div>

			<div class="article-details-control-container">
				<div class="article-details-function" data-id="2576329">
					<a class="font-large-btn" onclick="FontSizeAdjust.change(1)" title="放大字體"><span data-icon="&#xe97f;" class="hket-icon-font-lg"></span></a>
